events.name: Startup Sauna Demo Day Fall ‘17
events.short_description:
There are accelerators and Demo Days. Startup Sauna’s Demo Days aren't your usual snoozefest; they’re a celebration of early-stage startups on their way to becoming scaleups, and we are good at celebrating. 
 
Eurasia’s most intensive accelerator, Startup Sauna, brings its Demo Day to Slush 2017 to showcase the most impressing early-stage founders found from Finland, Russia, Ukraine, Switzerland, UK, and South Korea.

events.name: DO! GOES SLUSH
events.short_description:
Compete in our ‘DO! goes SLUSH'-competition and win a ticket for SLUSH!

SLUSH is the biggest tech start-up and investors conference in Europe and gathers more than 15 000 tech entrepreneurs, VC's and journalists. It takes place in Helsinki, Finland on November 30 - December 1st, 2017. Slush is the focal point for startups and tech talent to meet with top-tier international investors, executives and media. 

DO! will pay the conference passes for 2 UGent student-entrepreneurs (early-stage startup passes).
